WEBVTT


00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.580
One thing I love is submitting to my husband

00:00:02.760 --> 00:00:05.220
And not in an oppressive/toxic way,

00:00:05.320 --> 00:00:08.660
but in a we honor each other with love and devotion,

00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:10.880
I'm being taken care of kind of way.

00:00:10.881 --> 00:00:14.001
I'm not bashing other people who don't believe this,

00:00:14.002 --> 00:00:15.081
if you disagree,

00:00:15.082 --> 00:00:16.581
that is your right.

00:00:16.760 --> 00:00:21.440
But there’s something so special when you find a good man that's fully devoted to you,

00:00:21.441 --> 00:00:23.201
this is what a lot of women want,

00:00:23.202 --> 00:00:26.401
even when the world pressures you to be independent,

00:00:26.402 --> 00:00:28.501
I hear other women say all the time,

00:00:28.800 --> 00:00:30.400
“just wait until you get older”

00:00:30.401 --> 00:00:32.381
or “who's gonna tell her”

00:00:32.440 --> 00:00:35.720
But if this is what I value and other people value,

00:00:35.721 --> 00:00:39.581
why are we putting past relationship pain onto others?

00:00:39.880 --> 00:00:41.940
A woman's scorn is so valid

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:46.400
but I love submitting to my partner so he can properly lead us

00:00:46.401 --> 00:00:48.181
and I know I'll be happy.

00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:52.060
I’m not ashamed to say that I like traditional gender roles.

00:00:52.120 --> 00:00:54.380
I'm a woman who has long hair,

00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:55.520
I like to cook,

00:00:55.521 --> 00:00:58.361
clean, and nurture the ones I love.

00:00:58.362 --> 00:01:00.661
And I love being who I am.

00:01:00.680 --> 00:01:03.560
I think we should honor and respect being a housewife,

00:01:03.561 --> 00:01:07.361
but I also don't think that we need to tear down workforce women either.

00:01:07.362 --> 00:01:09.781
Everyone should pursue what's right for their lives.

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:14.860
true feminism doesn't or (shouldn't) care what other women do with their lives

00:01:14.960 --> 00:01:17.440
Radical feminist will demonize any woman

00:01:17.441 --> 00:01:19.861
who says that she wants to be a stay at home wife

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:23.460
and live by traditional roles in her marriage or household

00:01:23.760 --> 00:01:26.640
All I’m saying if you enjoy traditional roles; cooking,

00:01:26.641 --> 00:01:28.361
cleaning, etcetera,

00:01:28.362 --> 00:01:29.961
then you shouldn't be ashamed of it

00:01:29.962 --> 00:01:31.711
do whatever makes you happy.
